==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Missy
<hw>Mis"sy</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An affectionate, or contemptuous,
form of <xex>miss</xex>; a young girl; a miss.</def> --
<def2><pos>a.</pos> <def>Like a miss, or girl.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

